---
title: Smart Zesty Beyond Meat® Meatballs with Lemon-Garlic Sauce and Mini Wedges
description: Lemon zest gives these Beyond Meat® meatballs bright flavour and provides a nice balance for the lemon-garlic sauce. The creamy dill dressing on the side salad gives off Mediterranean vibes, while the mini potato wedges are just adorable.

